Changes since 0.1:
------------------

* Fixed XSS vulnerability allowing for arbitrary code execution
* Fixed directory traversal vulnerability allowing content to be read from outside the content path
* Added localisation support for all internal strings
* Added Finnish and English localisations
* Added AUTHORS file to track contributions
* Added CHANGES file to track release changes
* Added error handling for bad URLS, bad content paths and improperly detected articles
* Added id attributes to navigation menu items
* Added support for multiple CSS files
* Added support for multiple Javscript files
* Added config_default.php to ease upgrade process
* Added config.php option for enabling article timestamps
* Added config.php option for enabling article download links
* Updated README.md for 0.2 release
* Improved XHTML compliance 

